cbp_comments: EDTA ALQ 2 AND L.HEP ALQ 2 EMPTY

cbp_edta_aq1_noreason: No EDTA cord blood sample was collected.
cbp_edta_aq2_noreason: No EDTA cord blood sample was collected.
cbp_comments: Only Lith Hep cord blood tube was collected and no EDTA cord blood sample. Thus, no aliquots for EDTA plasma.

cbp_edta_aq1_noreason: The EDTA blood tube was found to be clotted upon arrival to the lab.
cbp_edta_aq2_noreason: The EDTA blood tube was found to be clotted upon arrival to the lab.
cbp_lithhep_aq1_noreason: The Lith Hep blood tube was found to be clotted upon arrival to the lab.
cbp_lithhep_aq2_noreason: The Lith Hep blood tube was found to be clotted upon arrival to the lab.
cbp_comments: Both EDTA and Lith Hep cord blood tubes were found to be clotted upon arrival to the lab and as a result, aliquots for the plasma unavailable.
L. Hep ALQ-2 is less than 1.0ml.

cbp_lithhep_aq1_noreason: Lith Hep sample tube hemolysed, hence plasma and pellets could not be separated.
cbp_lithhep_aq2_noreason: Lith Hep sample tube hemolysed, hence plasma and pellets could not be separated.
